{"tid":2092724,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"移民撚想證明自己仲愛香港既話，去到英國同我做一樣野.…....","createTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T20:08:26.000Z","uid":142025,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"517f44f82a9a7d422bd43d0db2d9bcd331087d3c","tid":2092724,"uid":142025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">參軍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你真係想光復香港，同解放軍/警犬生死相搏、武裝革命係必須發生既事。<br />\n<br />\n呢一年入面，我哋睇到共產黨係唔會同你講道理講條件，<span style=\"color: red;\">唯一會令共產黨屈服既就係武力，絕對既武力。</span><br />\n<br />\n做唔到既話就唔好撚同我講自己有幾愛香港。因為你哋只係一班剩係識嗌口號既蝗蟲。<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身BC，唔洗靠BNO移民<br />\n我會係香港戰至最後一刻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0d3f5980d222e2dd2ed395e454194f12cb7277e","tid":2092724,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"BNO有冇得直接參軍"},{"pid":"c2d4c116f91610a5bbb66d0aa13e04f704fc3a19","tid":2092724,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0d3f5980d222e2dd2ed395e454194f12cb7277e","tid":2092724,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"BNO有冇得直接參軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n詳情睇上班台"},{"pid":"4427d9caa3771ffc32613d24c4a62b36c2d591f6","tid":2092724,"uid":45977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0d3f5980d222e2dd2ed395e454194f12cb7277e","tid":2092724,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"BNO有冇得直接參軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"已經有BNO holder幾年前就做御林軍樂隊成員"},{"pid":"2a31cc98a200b22fd84dc3b87a913b18dd6fd14e","tid":2092724,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4427d9caa3771ffc32613d24c4a62b36c2d591f6","tid":2092724,"uid":45977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0